\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{z}_{n}$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
\mathbf{\mu}_{n|n-1} & = & \mathbf{F}\mathbf{\mu}_{n-1}\\
\mathbf{P}_{n|n-1} & = & \mathbf{F}\mathbf{P}_{n-1}\mathbf{F}^{T}+\int_{\tau=0}^{\Delta t}\exp(\mathbf{A}\tau)\mathbf{Q}\exp(\mathbf{A}\tau)^{T}d\tau
