where 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{F}=\exp\left(\mathbf{A}t\right)$
\end_inset

.
 To compute the integral, instead of using the Matrix Fraction Decomposition
 proposed in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "sarkka2019sde"
literal "false"

\end_inset

, we eliminate the covariance matrix 
